instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1637468584254501v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by kerem.tech", "description": "Claude is an AI assistant built by Anthropic. For cybersecurity engineers, it works like a second brain that knows every syntax, every framework, and every config format you deal with daily.\n\nInstead of reading documentation for Sigma, YARA, Kubernetes, or GitHub Actions every time you need to write a rule or config, you describe what you want in plain English and Claude generates production-ready output.\n\nJust go to claude.ai and start prompting.\n\nHere are 7 prompts every cybersecurity engineer should save:\nSigma Rule Generation: Sigma is a generic detection rule format that works across any SIEM. Describe the attack, get a deployable rule.\n\nYARA Rule Writing: YARA is a pattern-matching tool for identifying malware. Define your indicators, get a scanning rule.\nCIS Hardening Guide: CIS Benchmarks are the industry-standard security baselines for OS and cloud hardening. Pick your OS, get exact commands.\n\nIR Runbook: A runbook is a step-by-step incident response procedure. Name the scenario, get containment to recovery in minutes.\n\nK8s NetworkPolicy: NetworkPolicies control pod-to-pod traffic in Kubernetes clusters. Describe the segmentation, get a zero-trust YAML.\n\nCI/CD Security Pipeline: Security pipelines automate SAST, container scanning, and secret detection in your build process. List your tools, get a working workflow.\n\nAdversary Simulation Plan: Adversary simulation replicates real threat actor TTPs mapped to MITRE ATT&CK. Pick a threat group, get a full exercise plan.\n\nNo sensitive data needed in any prompt. No logs, no source code, no infrastructure details. You describe the intent, Claude handles the syntax.\n\nSave this for your next shift.\n\n#cybersecurity #claude #ai #blueteam #infosec", "duration": 8.08, "timestamp": 1775562718, "uploader_id": "54638301196", "uploader": "Kerem 🛡 Cyber Security Engineer", "channel": "kerem.tech", "like_count": 2786, "comment_count": 73, "comments": [{"author": "glbaor", "author_id": "9408859802", "id": "17948061807028690", "text": "🙌🙌", "timestamp": 1777830553}, {"author": "kraken_rasen", "author_id": "53720399347", "id": "18045355643539024", "text": "Why do you need AI for this? It is obvious basic security staff😮", "timestamp": 1777140632}, {"author": "jrequena69", "author_id": "1445752981", "id": "17898911766426474", "text": "Great", "timestamp": 1776974503}, {"author": "linux_sujith", "author_id": "74240825293", "id": "18093701117271976", "text": "🔥🙌", "timestamp": 1776830258}, {"author": "naresh__chowdary_7", "author_id": "7614693632", "id": "17970038871042387", "text": "🙌", "timestamp": 1776699758}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/660562708_18018912317821197_4890704951017490417_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi41NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEgj73Toe0EP3Jev8yML3grcgNM24TV0738aGF_Toe9b_6j8_vKhj-GAN1NnKLVSrm_LeJ1kQiYe7TscwxNaGmA&_nc_ohc=hhcHJj2BBwEQ7kNvwH8RdVw&_nc_gid=fsRQU5BmaovQciSATlfrDw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af74vS4PWknFDd7S1vB56lhFnoKLJjYmGHN7u84STpVoGA&oe=6A10FBBB&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/660562708_18018912317821197_4890704951017490417_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi41NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEgj73Toe0EP3Jev8yML3grcgNM24TV0738aGF_Toe9b_6j8_vKhj-GAN1NnKLVSrm_LeJ1kQiYe7TscwxNaGmA&_nc_ohc=hhcHJj2BBwEQ7kNvwH8RdVw&_nc_gid=fsRQU5BmaovQciSATlfrDw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af74vS4PWknFDd7S1vB56lhFnoKLJjYmGHN7u84STpVoGA&oe=6A10FBBB&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1333, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1